data-triple-N3.o: "Nottinghamshire County Cricket Club is one of the 18 major county clubs which make up the English and Welsh domestic cricket structure, representing the historic county of Nottinghamshire. Its limited overs team is called the Nottinghamshire Outlaws. Their kit colours are dark green with gold/yellow trim for the Clydesdale Bank 40 and more yellow dominant for Friends Life t20. The shirt sponsors are Capital One and Orchid IT."@en
